        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜ 納指回落　Nvidia業績靚仔仍跌 5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 納指回落 Nvidia業績靚仔仍跌 5%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"595\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9sDYo24BMawQ..gWzxHwrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5NQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/b727d2d0-135e-11f1-95fe-ec5392f3553b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 納指回落 Nvidia業績靚仔仍跌 5%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周四自早段更大跌幅中回穩，但整體仍告下跌。納數下跌1.2%；標普500指數下跌約0.6%；傳統股為主的道指則微升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Nvidia;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVDA/\">Nvidia</a>儘管上個財季利潤近翻倍勝預期，數據中心業務收入續增75%，仍未能令投資者驚喜，華爾街對人工智能的回報潛力及顛覆風險憂慮升溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Nvidia股價下跌逾 5%。儘管該晶片巨頭季度收入及盈利均大幅超越預期，並上調業績指引，但投資者反應平淡。集團對未來展望的推動因素缺乏細節，且未計及潛在的中國市場收入，令部分華爾街人士質疑其競爭壓力及人工智能建設需求的持續性。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-000db8c5-51f7-4275-b668-a7731c36c44e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月26日（星期四）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 升17.05點或0.03%，報49,499.2點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌37.27點或0.54%，報6,908.86點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌273.69點或1.18%，報22,878.38點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期油;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期油</ins></a> 收報65.47美元一桶，升0.05美元或0.08%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,201.5美元一盎司，跌24.7美元或0.47%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報67,375.67美元，跌1,789.57美元或2.58%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.017厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首次申領失業救濟人數輕微上升，顯示經濟增長略為停滯。投資者正等待明天公布的 1 月批發通脹數據，以評估聯儲局減息的可能性。聯儲局理事米蘭(Stephen Miran)周四表示，當局今年需要將利率降低約一個百分點，且指四次減息是合適。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場研究機構IDC預計，受記憶體晶片短缺影響，全球智能手機市場今年將收縮12.9%，形容是一場「前所未有的危機」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">電商平台<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:eBay;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/EBAY/\">eBay</a>表示，計劃裁員約800人，佔其全職員工總數的6%。 公司指，正採取措施對公司業務進行再投資，並調整組織架構以適應公司戰略重點，將影響到部分員工職位， eBay收市報升3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國與伊朗在日內瓦舉行第三輪核談判之際，市場對談判前景轉趨謹慎，軍事衝突風險再度成為焦點，國際油價微升。</p></div>",
